ype in <strong>ss1</strong>."]},"id":"f036abdc-f00c-4648-b042-2ad3aae030ef","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/fEgwEdd85cXoKttFBQt4sb.gif","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":" ","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/3994/linking-cells-f-5.gif","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/fEgwEdd85cXoKttFBQt4sb.gif","credit":"","align":"","id":"fEgwEdd85cXoKttFBQt4sb","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/fEgwEdd85cXoKttFBQt4sb.gif","alt":"Naming a spreadsheet"},"id":"e27b8185-7e39-481f-aea9-bae6027b4a42","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Let s set up a simple formula on spreadsheet ss2. In the A1 cell, enter <strong>5</strong>. Then in the B1 cell, enter <strong>4</strong>. Now add the two cells up by clicking in the C1 cell and then clicking the Formula tab and entering: <strong>=SUM(A1,B1)</strong>"]},"id":"7aa033b2-a3e9-4e5c-af33-b4c38ed12b4a","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/BDASTudf6Z4zRpTdVF8dyj.gif","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":" ","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/3994/linking-cells-f-4.gif","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BDASTudf6Z4zRpTdVF8dyj.gif","credit":"","align":"","id":"BDASTudf6Z4zRpTdVF8dyj","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/BDASTudf6Z4zRpTdVF8dyj.gif","alt":"Formula"},"id":"6e0a80f9-b445-48a2-9cb5-990dac7c3a43","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["You can now bring that C1 cell into your other spreadsheet, ss1. At the bottom of the screen, click on the ss1 spreadsheet. Add a link from C1 on ss2 to A1 on ss1. Click on A1 then click on the <strong>Insert </strong>tab on the ribbon. Select the <strong>Hyperlink</strong> icon.","In the address field, type in: <strong>=ss2!C1</strong>","You should now see the results of the ss2 spreadsheet in the A1 cell of the ss1 spreadsheet. "]},"id":"0ed9d791-503b-44ba-84f2-231ffe28321b","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/7UppZayF794tN9WdTYbREf.gif","link":{"href":"","